WEBVTT

00:14.400 --> 00:15.670
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

00:19.680 --> 00:25.060
[Xiangsheng Troupe]

00:25.780 --> 00:52.150
♪ Fires of war engulf
the frontier mountains ♪

00:57.350 --> 00:59.180
♪ From Yao Pass
rides a young woman general ♪

00:59.770 --> 00:59.840
♪ With delicately arched brows,
luminous eyes, and cherry-red lips ♪

00:59.840 --> 01:00.560
Let me do it!

01:02.960 --> 01:04.230
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

01:24.590 --> 01:27.700
♪ Who dares say a woman
cannot rival a man? ♪

01:28.600 --> 01:30.310
♪ The enemy general looms,
seven full feet of dread ♪

01:34.930 --> 01:36.340
♪ She answers with a thunderous war cry ♪

01:39.710 --> 01:41.070
Be a good pig in this life,

01:41.070 --> 01:43.130
and be a good person in your next life.

01:55.070 --> 01:55.920
It's done!

01:55.920 --> 01:58.979
There's a lot of blood—
bring another basin to catch it.

03:33.720 --> 03:38.740
[Pursuit of Jade]

03:38.860 --> 03:41.550
[Episode 1]

03:43.680 --> 03:45.470
We'll be ready to feast in a moment.

03:45.470 --> 03:46.590
-Great.
-Alright.

03:46.800 --> 03:47.870
No need to rush.

03:51.520 --> 03:53.800
Didn't the Fan family just have a funeral?

03:53.800 --> 03:55.240
Why did Mrs. Chen

03:55.240 --> 03:57.640
hire Changyu to slaughter
the New Year pig?

03:58.430 --> 04:00.030
Out of pity, of course.

04:00.590 --> 04:02.720
The Fan couple were killed by bandits,

04:02.750 --> 04:04.360
and they left behind no property—

04:04.360 --> 04:05.960
only two little girls.

04:06.630 --> 04:08.910
Luckily, Changyu is capable.

04:09.710 --> 04:11.240
She's following her father's trade,

04:11.240 --> 04:13.440
butchering pigs to support the family.

04:13.470 --> 04:15.870
She's held the family together
all on her own.

04:15.870 --> 04:17.040
Poor thing.

04:17.040 --> 04:19.100
The Fan couple were such good people.

04:19.269 --> 04:20.920
How did they meet such a fate?

04:20.950 --> 04:21.360
-Granny Kang.
-You're here.

04:21.360 --> 04:22.390
Come on, sit.

04:22.600 --> 04:25.160
It was all because of that girl.
She cursed them.

04:25.160 --> 04:26.160
Don't talk nonsense!

04:26.160 --> 04:27.600
Didn't I say it before?

04:28.510 --> 04:31.000
Look at how beautiful
Fan Erniu's wife was.

04:31.270 --> 04:31.870
Who knows,

04:32.110 --> 04:33.510
she might have come from a brothel.

04:33.510 --> 04:36.909
Otherwise, how would she ever marry
a butcher like Fan Erniu?

04:42.070 --> 04:43.310
Good heavens.

04:43.360 --> 04:44.800
Have respect for the dead.

04:44.800 --> 04:46.390
Let's not talk about it anymore.

04:46.390 --> 04:47.560
Am I wrong?

04:48.600 --> 04:50.000
She may take after her mother

04:50.000 --> 04:51.730
with all that delicate beauty,

04:52.070 --> 04:53.600
but she has such strength.

04:54.070 --> 04:55.120
Let alone a girl—

04:55.360 --> 04:56.600
even a young lad

04:56.680 --> 04:58.070
couldn't match her.

05:00.160 --> 05:01.360
She's really strong.

05:02.270 --> 05:03.270
That girl

05:03.310 --> 05:04.440
just has a hard fate.

05:04.510 --> 05:05.830
I didn't say that.

05:05.920 --> 05:07.950
Wasn't she engaged to Song Yan?

05:08.160 --> 05:09.270
The Song family

05:09.270 --> 05:11.360
went to have their birth charts matched,

05:11.360 --> 05:13.120
and when they saw the results...

05:13.120 --> 05:14.240
oh my.

05:14.600 --> 05:18.000
-She was born under a cursed star.
-I haven't heard of that.

05:18.830 --> 05:20.190
The Song family panicked and hurriedly

05:20.190 --> 05:21.160
called off the engagement.

05:21.160 --> 05:21.870
Is that so?

05:23.950 --> 05:24.800
Granny Kang,

05:25.120 --> 05:26.360
here's some pig blood for you.

05:26.360 --> 05:27.160
To help wash away your bad luck.

05:27.160 --> 05:28.160
You... you...

05:29.750 --> 05:31.550
Look at her! That's outrageous!

05:32.800 --> 05:33.390
Look at what she did to me!

05:33.390 --> 05:34.560
Mrs. Chen said

05:34.870 --> 05:37.390
that half of today's pig
is to be shared with the neighbors.

05:37.390 --> 05:39.450
Everyone, come and choose your cuts!

05:40.270 --> 05:41.240
Hey, you...

05:41.750 --> 05:42.920
Let's go, hurry.

05:44.630 --> 05:46.430
What did I say wrong?

05:46.680 --> 05:48.750
You... you are a jinx!

05:49.190 --> 05:50.270
You cursed your parents to death.

05:50.270 --> 05:51.870
-You drove your fiancé away!
-Come on, stop talking.

05:51.870 --> 05:53.720
Your sister was born sickly—

05:53.720 --> 05:54.920
that's also because of you!

05:54.920 --> 05:55.600
Alright.

05:55.600 --> 05:56.560
Well, look at her!

05:56.560 --> 05:57.950
Granny Kang, the pork!

06:00.040 --> 06:00.630
Don't snatch!

06:00.630 --> 06:01.920
This piece is mine!

06:01.920 --> 06:03.390
This piece is mine!

06:20.360 --> 06:21.190
Changyu,

06:21.920 --> 06:23.920
here is the money
for butchering the pig today.

06:23.920 --> 06:24.750
Thank you, Mrs. Chen.

06:24.750 --> 06:26.040
The feast is about to start.

06:26.040 --> 06:27.190
Stay and eat with us.

06:27.750 --> 06:28.410
No, thanks.

06:29.270 --> 06:31.040
My family just had a funeral,

06:31.560 --> 06:33.800
and you didn't mind. Hiring me anyway

06:34.270 --> 06:35.800
was already more than kind.

06:36.560 --> 06:37.360
Alright then.

06:37.920 --> 06:39.720
Take the pork offal.

06:40.120 --> 06:41.120
Oh, I couldn't.

06:41.830 --> 06:42.750
Just take it.

06:43.600 --> 06:46.190
Your father used to make
the best master stock.

06:46.190 --> 06:48.480
Giving it to you won't be a waste.

06:49.040 --> 06:50.570
Take it home for Changning.

06:54.600 --> 06:55.200
Thank you.

06:56.159 --> 06:57.220
I'll head back now.

06:57.560 --> 06:59.560
Changning is waiting for me at home.

07:02.430 --> 07:03.160
Changyu!

07:04.240 --> 07:05.120
There's a war in Chongzhou,

07:05.120 --> 07:07.360
so it's not peaceful around here anymore.

07:07.360 --> 07:09.310
Be careful on your way home!

07:09.750 --> 07:10.480
Don't worry.

07:10.870 --> 07:12.630
I checked the almanac before leaving.

07:12.630 --> 07:13.560
It's a lucky day.

07:20.510 --> 07:21.950
What a good girl.

07:22.750 --> 07:23.630
It's a pity

07:24.000 --> 07:25.600
she has a hard life.

07:31.480 --> 07:34.000
Four, five, six...

07:34.390 --> 07:37.190
Ten, eleven, twelve...

07:37.630 --> 07:39.490
Fourteen, fifteen, eighteen...

08:22.360 --> 08:23.360
Sorry.

08:24.830 --> 08:27.070
I'm really sorry. Sorry.

08:28.480 --> 08:30.480
I didn't mean to. I really didn't.

08:31.000 --> 08:32.360
You've been a good pig in this life.

08:32.360 --> 08:33.390
Be a good person in the next life!

08:33.390 --> 08:34.510
I didn't mean to.

08:34.909 --> 08:37.169
Jade Emperor, Queen Mother of Heaven...

08:57.960 --> 08:59.090
He's not breathing?

09:01.320 --> 09:02.960
No... h-he's almost dead.

09:05.360 --> 09:06.030
Changyu,

09:06.550 --> 09:07.510
just go home.

09:12.390 --> 09:13.550
No, my family is poor.

09:13.550 --> 09:14.510
I don't have the money to save you.

09:14.510 --> 09:15.740
I still have a younger sister at home.

09:15.740 --> 09:17.510
What if you turn out to be a bad person?

09:17.510 --> 09:18.600
Changyu, don't be soft-hearted.

09:18.600 --> 09:19.960
Go home. Just go home.

09:19.960 --> 09:21.720
Go home. Go home!

09:22.270 --> 09:23.910
I'm coming to save you!

09:27.200 --> 09:28.000
Don't die!

09:28.770 --> 09:29.500
Don't die...

09:31.630 --> 09:32.760
Don't... It's okay.

09:38.080 --> 09:39.480
You've been a good pig in this life.

09:39.480 --> 09:41.280
Be a good person in the next life!

09:56.080 --> 09:57.000
Mother...

10:06.320 --> 10:08.780
It must be my mother
who wanted me to save you.

10:12.600 --> 10:13.480
Hold on.

10:14.000 --> 10:15.000
Please don't die.

10:16.000 --> 10:17.730
My mother wanted me to save you.

10:38.200 --> 10:39.120
Changning?

10:41.080 --> 10:42.550
Changning, open the door!

10:42.550 --> 10:43.360
Sister,

10:44.000 --> 10:46.320
I went to town to watch
a shadow play today.

10:46.320 --> 10:48.120
It was about a female general...

10:49.390 --> 10:50.030
Sister?

10:50.030 --> 10:51.830
Help me with the things outside.

10:59.360 --> 11:00.270
Changyu!

11:01.510 --> 11:02.710
Who are you carrying?

11:02.750 --> 11:03.910
I found him on the road.

11:03.910 --> 11:04.910
He had barely a breath left in him.

11:04.910 --> 11:06.910
Auntie Zhao, help me get him inside.

11:06.960 --> 11:07.360
You...

11:08.030 --> 11:09.320
You don't even know if he's good or bad,

11:09.320 --> 11:10.850
yet you dare bring him home?

11:11.000 --> 11:12.130
Besides, he is a man.

11:12.390 --> 11:13.910
You're an unmarried girl.

11:14.320 --> 11:16.120
People's gossip will drown you!

11:16.750 --> 11:18.610
No one saw you on the way, did they?

11:18.670 --> 11:19.790
His wounds look

11:20.390 --> 11:21.650
just like my parents'.

11:21.960 --> 11:24.290
He must've run into mountain bandits too.

11:25.480 --> 11:27.280
I can't worry about all that now.

11:28.270 --> 11:29.470
Carry him to my house.

11:29.960 --> 11:31.480
I can't bring bad luck to your home.

11:31.480 --> 11:32.750
What if he dies?

11:34.200 --> 11:35.200
Either he dies out there,

11:35.200 --> 11:36.270
or he dies in my house.

11:36.270 --> 11:36.800
Let's go.

11:38.120 --> 11:39.080
Come on!

11:43.270 --> 11:45.510
My husband went to the post station
at the town entrance on business.

11:45.510 --> 11:46.550
I have to go drag him back.

11:46.550 --> 11:47.750
You watch him for now.

11:47.910 --> 11:48.570
Changning,

11:48.670 --> 11:49.270
come here!

11:49.840 --> 11:51.150
You have to stay and watch him too.

11:51.150 --> 11:54.350
It's improper for an unmarried girl
to be alone with a man.

11:54.720 --> 11:55.670
I'll be back soon.

11:55.670 --> 11:56.360
Okay.

12:20.270 --> 12:21.730
Why is he bleeding so much?

12:23.510 --> 12:24.750
Before Mr. Zhao gets back,

12:24.750 --> 12:26.350
you absolutely must not die.

12:28.030 --> 12:31.560
I've gone out to treat patients
with Mr. Zhao before, after all.

12:32.600 --> 12:34.550
I have to try, even if it's a long shot.

12:34.550 --> 12:36.390
Changning, go fetch a bowl of hot water.

12:36.390 --> 12:37.320
Auntie Zhao said

12:37.320 --> 12:39.150
an unmarried woman and a man
shouldn't be alone together.

12:39.150 --> 12:40.200
I have to stay here and watch.

12:40.200 --> 12:41.390
Forget about that.

12:41.390 --> 12:42.750
He's about to die!

12:42.750 --> 12:43.480
Go, quickly!

12:56.240 --> 12:58.080
Last time, I used this much.

12:58.910 --> 13:00.870
But he's bleeding more this time.

13:03.390 --> 13:04.520
Better to add it all.

13:17.480 --> 13:18.940
What's going on, Changyu?

13:19.480 --> 13:20.030
He...

13:26.670 --> 13:27.750
What are you doing?

13:27.790 --> 13:29.050
Feeding him medicine.

13:29.720 --> 13:30.270
You...

13:30.440 --> 13:31.670
What the hell?

13:31.670 --> 13:34.030
You poured the whole pack of medicine in?

13:34.030 --> 13:36.440
Are you trying to save him or kill him?

13:36.440 --> 13:38.670
What are you doing, kid?

13:40.270 --> 13:41.120
I thought

13:41.480 --> 13:43.080
since last time there wasn't
as much bleeding,

13:43.080 --> 13:44.600
I'd use more this time.

13:46.080 --> 13:47.630
Last time it was a donkey!

13:48.030 --> 13:48.750
A donkey!

13:48.910 --> 13:50.510
Is that the same as a human?

13:51.320 --> 13:53.240
With a whole bowl of that forced down,

13:53.240 --> 13:54.240
forget a person—

13:54.240 --> 13:56.630
even a full-grown donkey would drop dead!

13:57.840 --> 13:59.480
Why are you yelling?

14:00.480 --> 14:02.150
I just wanted to save him.

14:02.670 --> 14:04.730
I didn't want him to die in your house,

14:04.870 --> 14:06.870
so I added a bit more medicine.

14:07.030 --> 14:08.320
Eating too much can burst your stomach.

14:08.320 --> 14:09.750
Then why don't you eat until you burst?

14:09.750 --> 14:11.270
You can die from eating?

14:12.550 --> 14:13.510
Alright, alright.

14:13.510 --> 14:14.640
You two go out first.

14:15.000 --> 14:16.720
Girls should wait outside.

14:25.030 --> 14:27.690
Changyu can barely
feed herself and her sister.

14:27.840 --> 14:29.510
What is she thinking,
bringing a strange man home?

14:29.510 --> 14:31.360
Why didn't you stop her?

14:32.790 --> 14:34.000
Look at that face,

14:34.000 --> 14:34.910
and you'll know why.

14:34.910 --> 14:36.040
How could I stop her?

14:36.080 --> 14:37.630
What use is a pretty face?

14:37.910 --> 14:39.710
It doesn't put food on the table.

14:53.240 --> 14:55.480
That big brother is so handsome.

14:55.630 --> 14:57.840
That's why you carried him back, right?

14:58.670 --> 14:59.510
Nonsense.

14:59.790 --> 15:01.390
I was just trying to save him.

15:01.670 --> 15:03.600
It has nothing to do with his looks.

15:37.510 --> 15:40.390
The scouts have tracked them
all the way here from Chongzhou.

15:40.390 --> 15:42.520
The blood trail disappeared here too.

15:42.630 --> 15:43.960
It snowed for a day and a night,

15:43.960 --> 15:45.890
so the footprints are all covered.

15:46.750 --> 15:47.070
This is Jizhou.

15:47.070 --> 15:48.200
[Wei Sheng]

15:48.200 --> 15:49.790
He Jingyuan's turf.

15:50.480 --> 15:52.550
We cannot search without permission.

15:52.550 --> 15:54.840
Report this back to the capital.
Let the Prime Minister decide.

15:54.840 --> 15:55.440
Let's head back.

15:55.440 --> 15:55.990
Yes, sir.

15:56.010 --> 15:56.550
Yes, sir.

16:05.510 --> 16:09.240
[Chunfeng Tofu Shop]

16:17.690 --> 16:24.360
[Xigu Lane]

16:24.360 --> 16:25.620
Changyu, you're back.

16:26.200 --> 16:26.910
Changyu.

16:29.790 --> 16:30.790
Changyu!

16:30.790 --> 16:32.240
Changyu, please wait!

16:36.840 --> 16:37.910
Changyu.

16:40.360 --> 16:41.840
Haven't seen you in half a month,

16:41.840 --> 16:44.670
and you've only grown more beautiful.

16:46.440 --> 16:47.040
This is...

16:47.720 --> 16:51.390
This is the medicine
you just bought for Changning?

16:51.600 --> 16:52.360
I have some...

16:52.360 --> 16:53.960
Just say what you want to say.

16:55.240 --> 16:56.630
I was just thinking

16:57.120 --> 16:58.650
your engagement with my son

16:58.670 --> 17:00.150
was already called off.

17:00.550 --> 17:03.510
So, it's useless for you
to keep that betrothal letter.

17:03.510 --> 17:06.109
-How about...
-You want the betrothal letter?

17:06.829 --> 17:07.589
Fine.

17:08.240 --> 17:09.720
Let's settle the accounts first.

17:09.720 --> 17:12.920
Over these years, my family paid
tuition fees for Song Yan

17:13.109 --> 17:15.170
and gave financial aid to both of you—

17:15.510 --> 17:16.829
settle those accounts,

17:16.829 --> 17:18.359
and I'll return the letter.

17:18.550 --> 17:21.349
You can't blame us
for calling off the engagement.

17:21.400 --> 17:23.930
That fortune teller said
your fate is cursed!

17:24.109 --> 17:25.510
I can't let my Yan marry a woman like you

17:25.510 --> 17:27.640
who brings misfortune to her husband!

17:28.109 --> 17:29.640
If we're talking about debts,

17:29.640 --> 17:31.350
we owe your parents,

17:31.550 --> 17:32.960
not you.

17:33.400 --> 17:35.270
My father signed that betrothal letter
with you.

17:35.270 --> 17:37.790
Then go down to the underworld
and ask him yourself.

17:37.790 --> 17:38.850
You wretched girl!

17:39.480 --> 17:40.480
Stop right there!

17:40.480 --> 17:41.000
Mother.

17:48.070 --> 17:49.070
Please calm down.

17:50.110 --> 17:50.970
It's better...

17:53.640 --> 17:55.550
if I explain things to her.

17:57.750 --> 17:59.000
Yan,

17:59.270 --> 18:00.720
that wretched girl...

18:00.830 --> 18:02.890
she's just after your official rank.

18:03.110 --> 18:05.750
She knows you're soft-hearted
and easy to manipulate.

18:05.750 --> 18:07.480
That's why she won't let you go.

18:07.550 --> 18:10.510
She's using past favors
to demand repayment!

18:12.240 --> 18:13.000
In a few days,

18:13.000 --> 18:13.960
-Using past favors...
-the County Magistrate

18:13.960 --> 18:15.200
will come to escort us to our new home.

18:15.200 --> 18:15.880
To demand repayment?

18:15.880 --> 18:16.400
-Mother.
-By then,

18:16.400 --> 18:18.600
-she'll pay for this.
-Let's go inside.

18:27.480 --> 18:28.160
Changyu,

18:29.000 --> 18:31.260
I, Song Yan, am not an ungrateful person.

18:32.150 --> 18:34.880
I have always remembered
your family's kindness.

18:34.880 --> 18:36.550
But of all virtues,
filial piety comes first.

18:36.550 --> 18:38.590
If I defied my mother
and insisted on marrying you,

18:38.590 --> 18:41.050
I'd become an unfilial
and unrighteous man.

18:42.110 --> 18:43.550
Although we cannot
become husband and wife,

18:43.550 --> 18:45.160
we can be like brother and sister.

18:45.160 --> 18:46.750
I'll take what you just said

18:47.070 --> 18:48.240
as mere words spoken in anger.

18:48.240 --> 18:49.350
I won't take them to heart.

18:49.350 --> 18:49.920
Don't.

18:51.000 --> 18:52.750
You must take them to heart.

18:53.270 --> 18:55.930
And there's no need
to speak of being my brother.

18:56.000 --> 18:58.510
Even between real brothers,
accounts must be clear.

18:58.510 --> 18:59.920
What I hate most

19:00.640 --> 19:03.100
are those who gossip
behind people's backs,

19:03.590 --> 19:05.450
spreading rumors that I'm a jinx,

19:05.880 --> 19:07.880
that my family is trading favors
for marriage,

19:07.880 --> 19:10.140
and that I'm forcing Song Yan to marry me!

19:10.720 --> 19:12.110
Others said those things!

19:12.110 --> 19:13.310
What does that have to do with us?

19:13.310 --> 19:14.830
I never mentioned your name,

19:14.830 --> 19:16.880
so why are you in such a rush to admit it?

19:16.880 --> 19:18.200
-You wretched girl...
-Mother!

19:18.200 --> 19:18.790
Changyu,

19:19.200 --> 19:21.000
I don't care what outsiders think.

19:21.000 --> 19:22.920
But the feelings between us
all these years—

19:22.920 --> 19:24.790
can they truly be weighed only in
silver and gold?

19:24.790 --> 19:26.920
Yes, they can only be weighed that way!

19:28.310 --> 19:31.310
You give me the money,
and I give you the betrothal letter.

19:31.310 --> 19:33.910
Don't disgust me with your talk
of "feelings."

19:34.000 --> 19:36.070
Raising two pigs would have been better
than knowing you!

19:36.070 --> 19:36.790
You...

19:38.880 --> 19:40.440
are nothing but ingrates.

19:41.200 --> 19:42.510
What did you say?

19:43.240 --> 19:44.350
You wretched girl,

19:44.480 --> 19:46.000
watch your mouth!

19:46.000 --> 19:47.240
-You are a pig!
-Mother.

19:47.240 --> 19:48.830
-Your whole family are pigs!
-Mother.

19:48.830 --> 19:50.490
No wonder you slaughter pigs!

19:50.790 --> 19:52.160
What nonsense is this?

19:53.750 --> 19:55.110
The old saying is right—

19:55.880 --> 19:57.080
spending money on men

19:57.270 --> 19:58.920
only invites divine punishment.

19:58.920 --> 20:01.270
There's still a man lying in the room!

20:02.920 --> 20:03.850
You startled me.

20:07.110 --> 20:07.440
Here.

20:08.510 --> 20:10.000
Those packs must have cost enough

20:10.000 --> 20:11.930
to attract divine punishment, eh?

20:14.480 --> 20:15.160
Changyu.

20:16.110 --> 20:16.920
That young man is awake.

20:16.920 --> 20:18.400
Go and check on him.

20:19.000 --> 20:19.880
Really?

20:20.960 --> 20:22.510
I thought he was a goner!

20:23.030 --> 20:24.490
Mr. Zhao, you're amazing!

20:24.590 --> 20:27.450
You're a miracle worker
for all sorts of creatures!

20:30.550 --> 20:31.550
Is that a compliment

20:31.550 --> 20:32.590
or a jab?

20:41.000 --> 20:41.880
You're awake.

21:09.830 --> 21:10.510
I...

21:11.000 --> 21:12.730
I saw you collapsed in the snow,

21:13.030 --> 21:14.510
so I carried you back.

21:15.200 --> 21:17.070
But the one who truly saved you
from death's door

21:17.070 --> 21:17.960
is Mr. Zhao.

21:20.920 --> 21:22.520
He changed your clothes too.

21:25.830 --> 21:26.830
This is his home.

21:28.750 --> 21:29.880
He is a doctor.

21:30.200 --> 21:31.750
He treats mules and horses.

21:33.480 --> 21:34.960
People too, of course.

21:41.200 --> 21:42.030
Thank you.

21:44.400 --> 21:45.920
When you carried me back,

21:47.030 --> 21:48.510
did you see anyone else?

21:48.750 --> 21:49.720
Anyone else?

21:51.510 --> 21:52.830
No, it was just you.

21:52.960 --> 21:55.420
There were others
buried in that snowdrift?

22:11.880 --> 22:13.210
I'll get you some water.

22:14.880 --> 22:15.310
Here.

22:19.070 --> 22:20.440
Where am I?

22:23.270 --> 22:26.000
This is Xigu Lane, Lin'an Town,
Qingping County.

22:26.960 --> 22:29.160
You don't look like
you're from around here.

22:29.160 --> 22:30.220
Where are you from?

22:30.480 --> 22:31.310
What's your name?

22:31.310 --> 22:32.790
Did you run into bandits?

22:38.160 --> 22:39.200
I'm Yan Zheng.

22:40.590 --> 22:41.920
"Yan" stands for words,

22:42.440 --> 22:44.240
and "Zheng" for righteousness.

22:44.590 --> 22:47.400
I fled here as a refugee from Chongzhou.

22:51.240 --> 22:52.840
Do you have any other family?

23:15.750 --> 23:16.790
All Solus.

23:18.400 --> 23:19.440
"All Solus"?

23:20.960 --> 23:22.760
Your family isn't surnamed Yan?

23:23.160 --> 23:24.960
Is "All Solus" your stepfather?

23:28.510 --> 23:29.720
I mean,

23:30.030 --> 23:31.890
I'm the only one left in my family.

23:34.720 --> 23:35.640
I'm sorry.

23:36.680 --> 23:38.350
No wonder when I saved you,

23:39.110 --> 23:40.970
you kept calling for your mother.

23:56.310 --> 23:57.200
Mr. Zhao!

23:57.680 --> 23:58.590
What's wrong? What's wrong?

23:58.590 --> 24:00.190
Why is he coughing like this?

24:00.510 --> 24:01.400
I don't know.

24:01.510 --> 24:02.310
I just mentioned his mother,

24:02.310 --> 24:03.550
and he started coughing!

24:03.550 --> 24:05.280
Why did you bring up his mother?

24:05.590 --> 24:08.030
You can't upset the patient
at a time like this.

24:08.030 --> 24:09.070
Oh, holy mother.

24:09.480 --> 24:10.940
You just mentioned it too.

24:13.590 --> 24:14.440
Look!

24:14.440 --> 24:16.370
Quick, help him lie down properly.

24:19.480 --> 24:20.310
Yan Zheng?

24:21.000 --> 24:22.000
Yan Zheng?

24:22.400 --> 24:23.240
Yan Zheng?

24:24.450 --> 24:26.310
[Yan]

24:26.310 --> 24:28.640
If he really dies because of my questions,

24:28.750 --> 24:29.720
what should I do?

24:30.720 --> 24:32.650
Even a simple coffin is expensive.

24:34.240 --> 24:35.110
How about

24:35.790 --> 24:37.320
I just dig a pit and bury him?

24:37.750 --> 24:38.590
Changyu,

24:38.790 --> 24:41.160
how about we ask the Heavens?

24:42.790 --> 24:43.480
That works.

24:44.440 --> 24:46.440
Good or bad, let the Heavens decide.

24:46.590 --> 24:48.650
Let's play the straw-snapping game.

24:50.880 --> 24:52.830
If I lose, I'll buy a coffin.

24:53.160 --> 24:54.830
If you lose, I'll dig a pit.

24:54.830 --> 24:55.480
Okay.

25:01.030 --> 25:02.230
Best two out of three.

25:05.350 --> 25:06.610
Three rounds maximum.

25:06.790 --> 25:07.310
Again.

25:10.680 --> 25:12.200
The Heavens said three times,

25:12.200 --> 25:13.310
"Buy a coffin."

25:13.790 --> 25:15.350
My money pouch says...

25:17.350 --> 25:18.030
dig a pit.

25:29.110 --> 25:29.920
Mr. Zhao.

25:30.400 --> 25:32.470
Don't blame yourself
if you can't save him.

25:32.470 --> 25:33.680
It's his own fate.

25:36.790 --> 25:37.750
What is this?

25:39.160 --> 25:40.640
My sister is stingy.

25:40.640 --> 25:44.100
The Heavens told her to buy a coffin
for that handsome brother,

25:44.160 --> 25:46.070
but she insists on
digging a pit just to get by.

25:46.070 --> 25:47.530
I'm not just "getting by."

25:47.640 --> 25:49.050
I even made him a memorial tablet.

25:49.050 --> 25:50.460
Look, "Yan Zheng."

25:51.220 --> 25:51.900
Luckily,

25:52.160 --> 25:54.160
I know how to write both characters.

25:56.480 --> 25:58.920
Throw this unlucky thing away immediately!

25:58.920 --> 26:01.250
That young man has a strong constitution.

26:02.030 --> 26:03.110
Plus, last night

26:03.240 --> 26:05.160
you fed him some hemostatic decoction,

26:05.160 --> 26:06.720
and he coughed up
a mouthful of clotted blood.

26:06.720 --> 26:08.350
His life is saved!

26:08.680 --> 26:09.960
That's great!

26:10.480 --> 26:11.440
His life is saved!

26:11.440 --> 26:14.030
His life is saved. His life is saved.

26:14.110 --> 26:15.880
Don't celebrate too early, you two.

26:15.880 --> 26:17.340
From here on, the medicine

26:17.350 --> 26:19.150
will cost more than that coffin.

26:19.960 --> 26:20.720
Changning.

26:21.880 --> 26:22.640
We're having noodles tonight.

26:22.640 --> 26:23.570
Go to the kitchen

26:23.960 --> 26:25.640
and fetch me half a basin of master sauce.

26:25.640 --> 26:26.480
Okay.

26:29.680 --> 26:31.240
Changyu, come here.

26:34.480 --> 26:36.110
What are you thinking?

26:37.680 --> 26:39.310
Changning has always been in poor health

26:39.310 --> 26:40.500
and is still taking medicine.

26:40.500 --> 26:42.960
Where will you get the extra money
for his medicine?

26:42.960 --> 26:44.070
Does that young man

26:44.350 --> 26:46.070
have any family left?

26:47.030 --> 26:48.110
He's "all Solus."

26:49.550 --> 26:50.880
-He's what?
-He's what?

26:52.510 --> 26:54.240
He said his whole family is dead.

26:54.240 --> 26:55.500
He's the only one left.

26:55.790 --> 26:57.390
He fled here from Chongzhou.

26:57.750 --> 27:00.000
He ran into bandits at Huchakou.

27:00.510 --> 27:01.480
Right now,

27:02.400 --> 27:04.400
I'm afraid he has nowhere else to go.

27:04.590 --> 27:05.680
Does he have

27:05.920 --> 27:07.440
any money on him

27:07.440 --> 27:08.590
or a travel permit?

27:08.960 --> 27:10.110
When I changed his clothes,

27:10.110 --> 27:10.830
I checked everything.

27:10.830 --> 27:11.830
Not a single coin.

27:12.390 --> 27:13.260
Either

27:13.680 --> 27:15.350
the bandits robbed him clean,

27:15.590 --> 27:17.400
or he's just a pauper himself.

27:21.350 --> 27:23.440
How about we carry him to
the county government office?

27:23.440 --> 27:25.440
Let the officials decide what to do.

27:25.640 --> 27:26.200
No way.

27:26.510 --> 27:28.270
There are so many beggars
lying outside that office.

27:28.270 --> 27:29.680
Have you ever seen them care?

27:29.680 --> 27:30.480
That's right.

27:31.110 --> 27:33.240
If he were dead, we could just bury him.

27:33.400 --> 27:36.060
But since he's alive,
we can't just abandon him.

27:38.920 --> 27:40.400
Let him recover here first.

27:40.400 --> 27:41.350
As for money,

27:42.110 --> 27:43.640
I'll figure something out.

27:50.870 --> 27:53.720
[Xigu Lane]

27:53.720 --> 27:56.350
The weather is dry.

27:57.240 --> 27:59.740
Beware of fire hazards!

27:59.740 --> 28:04.820
[Fill Your Belly]

28:06.420 --> 28:11.200
[Fill Your Belly]

28:15.480 --> 28:19.070
Two, four, six, eight, ten.

28:21.960 --> 28:23.750
Five, ten, eleven...

28:44.830 --> 28:45.590
Mother,

28:46.310 --> 28:48.710
if it's really you
who wanted me to save him,

28:49.110 --> 28:50.970
should I see it through to the end?

28:57.790 --> 28:59.070
What should I do?

29:39.050 --> 29:42.310
[Lin'an]

29:42.460 --> 29:44.070
[Luo's Pawnshop]

29:44.070 --> 29:45.110
One tael?

29:45.680 --> 29:47.640
This hairpin is made of pure silver!

29:47.640 --> 29:49.510
My father spent almost four taels on it!

29:49.510 --> 29:51.570
Well, this hairpin is indeed silver,

29:51.790 --> 29:54.310
but I can only give you
one tael and five mace.

29:54.720 --> 29:56.880
If it weren't for
what happened to your family,

29:56.880 --> 29:59.070
you wouldn't get
any more than this anywhere...

29:59.070 --> 29:59.640
Wait...

29:59.640 --> 30:00.270
Wait, wait, wait!

30:00.270 --> 30:01.240
Don't go!

30:01.590 --> 30:03.200
We can still negotiate.

30:07.550 --> 30:08.270
Two taels!

30:08.920 --> 30:10.070
Not one coin less!

30:11.880 --> 30:13.010
Alright, come back.

30:13.510 --> 30:16.030
Since we're neighbors in Xigu Lane,

30:16.230 --> 30:18.090
I'll do it to earn some good karma.

30:18.920 --> 30:20.450
Put your fingerprint here.

30:21.270 --> 30:22.800
I'll definitely redeem it.

30:23.310 --> 30:24.770
It's very important to me.

30:24.790 --> 30:25.960
Rest assured.

30:32.330 --> 30:35.790
[One silver hairpin pledged.
Two taels of silver granted.]

30:43.350 --> 30:44.960
As if it were a rare treasure.

30:48.960 --> 30:49.480
Go.

30:50.200 --> 30:50.960
Changyu,

30:51.590 --> 30:52.520
you bought pigs.

30:53.160 --> 30:55.290
Fan's Butcher Shop reopens tomorrow.

30:55.790 --> 30:57.920
Everyone, please come and support us!

30:57.920 --> 30:58.720
She's the boss now.

30:58.720 --> 30:59.720
Sure, sure.

31:01.030 --> 31:01.640
Changyu!

31:03.590 --> 31:04.160
Mr. Li?

31:04.680 --> 31:05.440
Are you...

31:05.880 --> 31:07.550
taking over your father's business?

31:07.550 --> 31:09.280
I have to make a living, don't I?

31:09.510 --> 31:10.570
That's the spirit.

31:10.680 --> 31:10.800
Don't listen to what others say.

31:10.800 --> 31:12.000
[Li Deqin, Chef of Yixiang Restaurant]

31:12.000 --> 31:13.040
What's wrong with butchering pigs?

31:13.040 --> 31:14.310
Food makes no distinction
between men and women,

31:14.310 --> 31:15.840
and neither does hard work.

31:16.270 --> 31:17.070
Thank you, Mr. Li.

31:17.070 --> 31:17.640
Look.

31:18.000 --> 31:19.480
I used the pig-selecting method
my father taught me

31:19.480 --> 31:20.680
to choose these pigs.

31:20.960 --> 31:23.090
Look at this round rump and short tail.

31:23.270 --> 31:25.200
Pigs like this
have thick skin and rich fat.

31:25.200 --> 31:27.030
It will be top-quality pork!

31:27.030 --> 31:28.110
Since it's going to be top-quality pork,

31:28.110 --> 31:29.480
how could we not fight for it?

31:29.480 --> 31:31.310
Our Yixiang Restaurant
will order half a side!

31:31.310 --> 31:32.270
Thanks, Mr. Li!

31:32.720 --> 31:33.850
-Bye, Mr. Li!
-Okay!

31:34.400 --> 31:34.930
Let's go.

31:35.310 --> 31:35.830
Go.

31:37.960 --> 31:38.960
Shoo, shoo, shoo.

31:39.110 --> 31:40.110
Shoo, shoo, shoo.

31:40.440 --> 31:42.000
-Shoo, shoo, shoo.
-Changyu!

31:42.000 --> 31:42.920
Back from buying pigs?

31:42.920 --> 31:43.400
Yes.

31:43.400 --> 31:44.400
This pig is so fat.

31:45.590 --> 31:46.640
Shoo, shoo, shoo...

31:46.640 --> 31:47.200
Shoo...

31:55.680 --> 31:56.880
Good little piggies.

31:57.680 --> 31:58.790
Let's not block the way.

31:58.790 --> 31:59.680
Let's go.

32:05.680 --> 32:06.510
Come on. Move!

32:06.590 --> 32:07.120
Hurry up!

32:07.310 --> 32:08.830
Go. Get going. Go.

32:10.550 --> 32:11.110
Come on.

32:12.160 --> 32:13.160
Shoo, shoo, shoo.

32:13.880 --> 32:14.680
Let's go home.

32:56.880 --> 33:00.610
[Are you alright? Please reply promptly.]

33:05.810 --> 33:07.390
[Are you alright? Please reply promptly.]

33:33.470 --> 33:35.440
[Xigu Lane, Lin'an Town, Qingping County]

34:19.710 --> 34:21.239
A white-feathered falcon?

34:38.280 --> 34:39.360
Who threw this?

34:39.670 --> 34:40.730
It hurts like hell!

34:48.880 --> 34:50.610
Where did this stone come from?

34:51.510 --> 34:53.030
Which bastard hit me?

34:53.880 --> 34:55.480
I'll kill him!

34:55.710 --> 34:56.280
Let's go!

34:58.230 --> 34:59.590
You really haven't seen any?

34:59.590 --> 35:00.960
No, I am from this village.

35:00.960 --> 35:02.030
Anyone found sheltering refugees...

35:02.030 --> 35:02.840
will be imprisoned.

35:02.840 --> 35:03.840
Report truthfully.

35:03.840 --> 35:04.190
Rest assured, sir.

35:04.190 --> 35:05.920
-Check over there.
-Of course.

35:09.630 --> 35:10.760
-What happened?
-Cut the crap!

35:10.760 --> 35:12.280
How many households are left?

35:12.280 --> 35:12.800
Sir,

35:13.070 --> 35:15.710
should I take you to a doctor first?

35:15.710 --> 35:16.630
To hell with the doctor!

35:16.630 --> 35:17.670
You guys check the households ahead!

35:17.670 --> 35:18.330
-Yes!
-Yes!

35:26.550 --> 35:28.190
Sir, what's going on?

35:28.550 --> 35:29.960
They're going door to door,

35:29.960 --> 35:33.760
searching for refugees
without household registration document.

35:34.480 --> 35:35.340
That scared me.

35:35.630 --> 35:37.960
I thought they were collecting grain tax.

35:39.360 --> 35:41.190
Why the sudden check for refugees?

35:41.190 --> 35:42.590
They're going to arrest all the refugees

35:42.590 --> 35:44.550
and send them to
the Chongzhou battlefield.

35:44.550 --> 35:45.880
The war there is critical.

35:45.880 --> 35:48.710
Once taken, they'll be placed in
the vanguard battalion.

35:48.710 --> 35:50.070
What's the vanguard battalion?

35:50.070 --> 35:51.200
Is that impressive?

35:51.400 --> 35:52.590
They're sent to die.

36:10.800 --> 36:11.400
Yan Zheng,

36:11.880 --> 36:15.480
do you have a travel permit
or household registration document?

36:18.110 --> 36:18.710
Yes.

36:20.840 --> 36:21.710
But I lost them.

36:22.800 --> 36:23.600
You lost them?

36:25.000 --> 36:26.150
Look for them again.

36:26.920 --> 36:28.070
Have you checked your clothes?

36:28.070 --> 36:29.670
When you changed my clothes,

36:29.710 --> 36:31.550
didn't you go through everything on me?

36:31.550 --> 36:32.110
I...

36:35.510 --> 36:37.150
I did that to save you.

36:37.440 --> 36:38.710
Don't misunderstand.

36:40.510 --> 36:41.770
Wait, how did you know?

36:42.110 --> 36:42.710
You...

36:44.710 --> 36:46.670
This isn't the time to talk about this.

36:46.670 --> 36:48.030
If you don't have a travel permit
or household registration document,

36:48.030 --> 36:49.230
you'll be taken as a refugee

36:49.230 --> 36:51.560
and sent to die in the vanguard battalion!

36:56.400 --> 36:57.400
What should we do?

36:57.590 --> 36:58.990
The soldiers are coming.

36:59.550 --> 37:01.150
Since the soldiers are here,

37:01.960 --> 37:03.620
I can't stay and cause trouble

37:04.000 --> 37:05.110
for you.

37:16.550 --> 37:17.480
I've got an idea.

37:19.030 --> 37:20.360
There's a place to hide.

37:22.320 --> 37:23.120
Open the door.

37:24.190 --> 37:24.880
Open up!

37:25.960 --> 37:26.760
Open the door!

37:32.360 --> 37:34.220
Community Head, what's going on?

37:37.280 --> 37:38.030
Changyu,

37:38.550 --> 37:40.070
are you the only one home?

37:41.960 --> 37:43.920
Sir, this is the Fan's household.

37:44.800 --> 37:47.200
It's connected to the Zhao family's place.

37:49.320 --> 37:51.450
Are there any strangers staying here?

37:52.000 --> 37:52.760
No.

37:53.400 --> 37:54.630
It's a small town.

37:55.030 --> 37:57.110
Everyone knows each other.

37:57.840 --> 37:59.800
We'd notice
even an extra stray cat or dog.

37:59.800 --> 38:01.260
There's no stranger here.

38:03.280 --> 38:03.760
No one.

38:06.280 --> 38:07.210
-No one.
-No one.

38:07.920 --> 38:08.480
No one.

38:14.510 --> 38:15.110
Captain!

38:19.030 --> 38:19.890
Captain, look.

38:22.510 --> 38:23.710
What's with

38:24.360 --> 38:25.820
this bloodstained cloth?

38:26.000 --> 38:26.920
Explain!

38:28.360 --> 38:30.070
Who is injured in your house?

38:30.150 --> 38:31.280
No one is injured.

38:32.320 --> 38:33.440
I'm a butcher.

38:33.670 --> 38:35.270
It's a rag for wiping knives.

38:35.480 --> 38:37.630
I just slaughtered a pig a few days ago.

38:38.550 --> 38:39.880
A rag for wiping knives?

38:41.670 --> 38:43.230
You two, guard the front courtyard!

38:43.230 --> 38:43.800
The rest of you,

38:43.800 --> 38:44.530
come with me!

38:51.320 --> 38:51.960
Sir,

38:52.230 --> 38:55.290
the Fan family used to make a living
by butchering pigs.

38:57.230 --> 38:58.760
Can a young lady like you

38:59.070 --> 39:00.870
slaughter a pig all by yourself?

39:03.000 --> 39:03.840
Do you know

39:03.840 --> 39:06.110
that hiding refugees is a felony,

39:06.190 --> 39:07.520
tantamount to treason?

39:07.800 --> 39:09.660
Your whole family could be exiled

39:09.670 --> 39:10.670
or conscripted!

39:11.670 --> 39:12.440
Sir,

39:13.480 --> 39:14.880
my parents are dead.

39:16.110 --> 39:17.070
It's just

39:17.400 --> 39:19.530
my younger sister and me in the family.

39:21.110 --> 39:21.840
Changyu.

39:22.920 --> 39:23.590
Come here.

39:24.920 --> 39:26.670
Did you really hide a refugee?

39:28.030 --> 39:29.480
If you harbor anyone,

39:29.760 --> 39:31.960
10 households will be punished together.

39:31.960 --> 39:33.670
You don't want your neighbors

39:33.840 --> 39:35.840
to suffer with you, do you?

39:36.630 --> 39:38.920
If you hand the person over now,

39:38.960 --> 39:40.840
I can still put in a word for you.

39:41.760 --> 39:44.360
We'll say you were coerced by him.

39:59.030 --> 39:59.760
Stand ready!

40:13.280 --> 40:14.880
The soldiers have found you!

40:15.960 --> 40:16.560
Come here.

40:18.600 --> 40:19.070
[Fan]

40:19.070 --> 40:20.440
Sorry, sir!

40:20.710 --> 40:22.710
My sister and I were
playing hide-and-seek.

40:22.710 --> 40:24.190
You came so suddenly,

40:24.320 --> 40:26.920
and I didn't have time to call her
out of hiding.

40:30.480 --> 40:31.150
No one.

40:31.960 --> 40:32.590
No one.

40:34.190 --> 40:35.670
[Fan]

40:35.670 --> 40:36.280
All right!

40:36.550 --> 40:37.920
Let's go check the next household!

40:37.920 --> 40:38.450
Let's go!

40:44.960 --> 40:47.020
You, go search the pigsty over there.

40:47.760 --> 40:48.290
Yes, sir.

40:51.630 --> 40:53.230
Why do I have to search this?

40:55.230 --> 40:57.490
What is there to search in a lousy pigsty?

41:17.150 --> 41:18.960
Sir, watch out. The pigs bite.

41:28.070 --> 41:31.070
Sir, watch your step—
there's pig offal on the ground!

41:35.520 --> 41:37.320
No one here! There's no one here!

41:37.320 --> 41:37.380
Just two pigs!

41:37.380 --> 41:39.270
[Fan]

41:44.840 --> 41:46.630
Changning, go lock the gate.

41:54.670 --> 41:54.960
It's me.

41:54.960 --> 42:03.360
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

42:03.360 --> 42:04.110
I'm coming.

42:05.670 --> 42:15.260
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

42:16.300 --> 42:19.840
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

42:19.840 --> 42:20.960
